text: Sar-I-Ab railway station(, Balochi:سر آب ریلوے اسٹیشن) is located in Sar-I-Ab village, Quetta district of Balochistan province in Pakistan. ==See also== * List of railway stations in Pakistan * Pakistan Railways ==References== ==External links== *Official Web Site of Pakistan Railways Category:Railway stations in Quetta District Category:Railway stations on Quetta–Taftan Railway Line Category:Railway stations on Rohri–Chaman Railway Line
